lead_paragraph: Paris' police chief said on Monday he would be receiving thousands of reinforcements ahead of the Euro 2016 soccer tournament and that his force was as prepared as it could be to face the risk of a militant attack in the French capital.

headline.print_headline: 'We're Prepared', Says Paris Police Chief Ahead of Euro 2016
headline.main: 'We're Prepared', Says Paris Police Chief Ahead of Euro 2016
